## PUBLIC client-side config (safe to commit)
## Anything prefixed with VITE_ is bundled into the browser.
## Real secrets (Stripe secret keys, Supabase service role, Resend API key) must live in Vercel/Supabase dashboards.

VITE_SITE_URL=http://localhost:5173

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

## Testing Sandbox (server-only; do not commit)
